 magnate gores was estimated in  by forbes to be the thrichest american with a  billion fortune he founded the beverly hills california based platinum equity llc in  with the intent to acquire noncore divisions of fortune  corporations platinum equity has since expanded its investment criteria to include publictoprivate transactions and acquisitions from private sellers since its founding the firm has acquired more than  companies in industries that include technology and it services manufacturing industrials distribution transportation and logistics and equipment rentals in  platinum equity was recognized as one of the largest and fastestgrowing private companies in america ranking  on forbes’ largest private companies list in  and  on the  and  los angeles business journal list of las largest private companies in  platinum equity rose to  on forbes’ largest private companies list due to a  increase in the firms revenue in  platinum ranked  on the los angeles business journal’s list of the largest private equity firms in los angeles pressedit gores was featured on the april  cover of mergers  acquisitions magazine as its “pro of the year”  in addition gores was featured on the summer  cover of csuite quarterly with an article entitled “tom gores on balancing family business and the detroit pistons”  detroit pistons ownershipedit on june   tom gores and platinum equity bought palace sports and entertainment pse the parent company of the pistons and their former arena the palace of auburn hills from karen davidson the wife of the late bill davidson becoming only the third owner in the franchises year history according to crains detroit business the final sale price was  million far lower than expected still it was a handsome return on davidsons original investment hed bought the team from founding owner fred zollner in  for  million soon after gores and platinum equity took ownership the pistons made several leadership changes including appointing dennis mannion to oversee operations of pse and the pistons and lawrence frank as head coach of the pistons frank was the former head coach of the new jersey nets now known as the brooklyn nets former pistons star joe dumars remained as president of basketball operations under gores ownership pse and the pistons have demonstrated an ongoing commitment to the detroit community through programs that include seats for soldiers which provides free tickets for pse events to us armed forces members and their families as well as come together a program celebrating community service leadership and volunteerism throughout michigan philanthropyedit tom gores supports several philanthropic organizations and serves on the board of trustees for the los angeles county museum of art lacma he was also a member of the board of directors at st josephs hospital and ucla medical center in  gores and platinum equity began making a series of donations to san diegoarea causes and institutions including the san diego state university school of journalism and media studies public broadcasting service kpbs the avid center junior achievement and the classroom of the future foundation tom gores and his family help to support childrens hospital los angeles and in particular the division of clinical immunology and allergy as a result the gores family allergy center at childrens hospital los angeles was formed to help provide comprehensive care and research in allergy gores and his brother alec donated  to genesee high school in honor of tom and julia joubrans th wedding anniversary in  since january   tom has pledged to help raise  million for the city of flint michigan as the lead crisis continues referencesedit  a b mark kurlyandchik new pistons owner tom gores aims high hour detroit retrieved july     httpwwwforbescomprofiletomgores  tom gores forbescom march  retrieved    letters san diego reader  retrieved  for the record my mother is of lebanese descent and my father was of greek descent we were raised and are still practicing catholics   jewish journal christian billionaires from israel looking to buy miramax by danielle berrin april    selfmade billionaire tom gores of tiny genesee could be next owner of detroit pistons mlivecom retrieved    pistons bidder shot for delphi  crains detroit business  detroit news and information crainsdetroitcom retrieved    tom gores platinum equity chairman and ceo platinumequitycom retrieved    platinum equity the firm platinumequitycom retrieved  may    americas largest private companies  platinum equity forbescom retrieved  june    list of las largest private companies la business journal retrieved  june    americas largest private companies of  forbescom retrieved  june     largest private equity firms in los angeles list pdf cbjonlinecom retrieved    unconventional wisdom tom gores sees value where others dont pdf mergers  acquisitions  retrieved    tom gores on balancing family business and the detroit pistons csuite quarterly summer  retrieved  may    karen davidson and tom gores reach agreement on sale of detroit pistons nbacom retrieved  june    shea bill  ‘shocking bargain gores pays  million for pistons crains detroit business   dennis mannion named president of the detroit pistons and palace sports  entertainment the detroit pistons retrieved  june    lawrence frank former nets coach hired by detroit pistons as head coach new jersey online  july  retrieved  june    joe dumars to remain pistons president under new ownership aol sporting news  april  retrieved  june    ‘seats for soldiers’ free ticket offer continues for designated events at the palace the oakland press retrieved  june    pistons announce come together community program nbacom retrieved  june    corporate responsibility platinumequitycom retrieved    lacma los angeles county museum of art lacmaorg retrieved   external linksedit homepage tom gores  twitter forbes world billionaires  platinum equity profile of tom v t e private equity and venture capital inves