 technology to deliver powerful unified communications features talking planet is built to be rapidly deployed as a private label service for clecs hosting companies and other communications value added resellers this solution includes a complete suite of customizable features including unlimited local and long distance calling caller id call waiting  way calling e video calling unified inbox followme service and voiceactivated dialing intelliverse was formed as a result of combining voicecom telecommunications llc a year veteran of the telecommunications industry providing call answering solutions for the businesstobusiness market and inuntius inc a voip pioneer with nine years of development in sipbased voip and unified communications solutions in november  voicecom acquired inuntius and since that time the combined entity has been working to quickly integrate technologies and operations so it can begin to bring its unique blend of internet and telephonybased services to the marketplace with its debut of talking planet intelliverse does just that about intelliverse a leading provider of communications services for the enterprise wholesale and small  medium business market sectors intelliverse specializes in creating industryspecific communications solutions to accomplish this intelliverse aligns sets of technologybased applications around specific business dynamics the result is a suite of valuedriven communications packages to address a customers specific business needs communications solved founded in  intelliverse offers the stability of an established company plus the agility of an innovative technology provider with over  years of experience intelliverse has solid technology foundations in voip ivr and messaging yet has learned that while technology is one thing technology applied is quite another intelliverse passionately listens to hears and responds to the daily and longterm needs of its clients around the world by developing solutions that recognize and address the issues important to its customers headquartered in atlanta intelliverse is a member of the gores group of companies and provides its services throughout north america the companys solutions are designed to meet a diversity of needs including automated selfservice  customer care interpersonal messaging and largescale corporate communications intelliverse delivers its solutions across a variety of industries including retail  manufacturing food services banking government organizations real estate and wholesale telecommunications more information can be found at wwwintelliversecom about the gores group llc founded in  the gores group is a private equity firm focused on acquiring controlling interests in mature and growing businesses which can benefit from the firms operating experience and flexible capital base the firm combines the operational expertise and detailed due diligence capabilities of a strategic buyer with the seasoned ma team of a traditional financial buyer the gores group has become a leading investor primarily in the technology and telecommunications sectors having demonstrated over time a reliable track record of creating substantial value in its portfolio companies alongside management headquartered in los angeles california the gores group maintains offices in boulder colorado and london for more information please visit wwwgorescom for additional information please contact intelliverse sandra jelovic marketing director   return to top back to news recent news the gores group completes the acquisition of triumph’s air repair business rebranded as turbineaero inc february   turbineaero inc featured at thailand board of investment’s “opportunity thailand ” conference february   the gores group acquires ami entertainment july   archives news                     contact the gores group los angeles t f   wilshire blvd beverly hills california  usa directions from lax airport directions from burbank airport boulder t f   lookout road boulder c